manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Minlu 4-in-1 Retractable Multi Charging Cable 4A The durability you’ve come to expect from Minlu 4 in 1 Charger Cord—now with universal compatibility. With Dual Phone, USB-C and Micro USB connectors built-in, it’s the only cable you’ll ever need. Features ● Length: 120cm (4Ft) ● Material: TPE + Aluminium Alloy ● Packing: 2 × 4 in 1 Retractbale Multi USB Cables Warm tips ● The maximum total output current of iP is 2.4A, USB-C is 3.0A and Micro-USB is 2.4A (For total, not for each end) ● The actual charging speed is determined by the highest output that the wall charger can provide, you can charge multiple devices at the same time with a 5V/2.4A–3.0A wall charger, particularly suitable for family or guests.

4Ft/120cm and 4 in 1 Retractable Design ● 4Ft/120cm is perfect length for long distance charging, 4-in-1 retractable design, makes the cord portable and only need one cable when you are on a business trip or traveling. 4-IN-1 Retractable Multiple Charging Cables ● USB 2.0: Universally compatible for Phone, Micro-USB & Type-C devices, it has 4 different ports to USB cable for your most needs, it can charge 4 devices at the same time. ● iOS-Ports: With charging and data transmission functions. Compatible with Phone 15 14 Plus/ 15 14 13 12 11 Pro Max/ 15 14 13 12 11 Pro/ 15 14 13 12 Mini/ SE/ 15 14 13 12 11/ XS/ XS Max/ XR/ 8/ 8 Plus/ 7/ 7 Plus/ 6s/ 6s Plus/ 6 Plus/ 6/ 5/ 5S, Pad Air/ Air 2, Pad Pro, Pad mini Pod touch. ● Type-C: Have charge function. Compatible with Samsung Galaxy UItra S23 S22 S21 S20 S10 S9 S8, New Book 2015, Book Pro 2016, ChromeBook Pixel 2015, Google Nexus 6P/5X, OnePlus 2/3/4/5, Huawei ,Moto z force,Moto z2 play/Google Pixel/XL/2/2 XL and more. ●Micro-USB: Have charge function. Compatible with most Android and Windows phones, tablets and many other devices including HTC/Nokia/LG/Sony/Bluetooth Speakers/Headphone/Earphone/MP4/MP3/PS/GPS device.

Charging Fast 4.0A & Syncing ● The thicker copper core wire inside can realize faster and more stable charging, which is 35% faster than ordinary multi cables. ● Only iOS connector support data transmission, 480 Mbps. Flexible And Durable Withstand 12,000+ bending. How to use? Please pull both side at the same time!!! Please pull both side at the same time!!! Please pull both side at the same time!!!

Simplify your life with MINLU retractable multi charger cable ● Organize Your Environment: Bid farewell to cable clutter and untidy desks. Maintain a clean and organized workspace by charging multiple devices using a single cable. ● NOTE: When charging multiple devices simultaneously, please use a 5V/3.0A (9V/2.0A) or 60W adapter.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 25, 2024
reviews.reviewText: This has always been great for in the car or traveling! I have another brand similar but they no longer sell on Amazon. I needed a few more and these were on sale. The idea of two of the iPhone chargers on one sold me. It came in and I tested it. It charged up multiple devices, as promised. But what sent me here to leave a review was the fact that my husband accidentally washed a load of laundry with this in it. We have no clue how it got in our hamper (we suspect our toddler did it) but my husband only realized when he went to switch the load to the dryer. We expected this was broken and we’re ready to toss it. But it was dry and I decided to test it. It still worked perfectly! Not many items can make it through a load of laundry and come out looking and working like it hadn’t. The only way I could confirm it actually got washed was because it smells like our detergent lol. I’m very impressed this held up through the washing machine. We’ll definitely buy this brand again when we need more in the future.

reviews.reviewText: I love that no matter what kind of phone you have, this charger will have you covered. I have these on our guest room so guests always jave the charger they need. They charge fast and are so convenient with the quick retractable cord. I have bought servers of them over the years.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 7, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Works for years!
reviews.reviewText: This is my second order of these (different seller - same product). As an Uber/Lyft driver with thousands of rides behind me, I get charging cable requests several times a week. I can extend this from the middle console to keep it from growing legs and walking off, and provide every type of charger someone could need. I gave one to a fellow driver and finally just repurchased these when I misplaced the other one on a recent trip. These will likely get lost long before they ever break.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 8, 2024
reviews.reviewText: These cables have worked great on all of my devises.At the same time I purchased these I purchased a Zeus X Go from a company called Futurizra at 4 times the cost for one which does not work with most of my items and they will not honor warranty.Stick with this MINLU Multi Charging Cable. It is excellent.Just remember to pull from both sides when winding or unwinding the cables.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 9, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect for use in my cars.
reviews.reviewText: The biggest problem with using phone charge cords in my car is that the cord is either too short or way too long. These retractable cords solve all my problems. I can make them the perfect length I need every time. And I can charge my devices that use different ports (lightning, USB-C, and USB Micro). And while most multi port charge cords like this are charge only (no data), this one allows data through the lightning port only (Apple car play works, but Android Auto does not), which was an unexpected bonus with these cables!
